>Description:
On my Ubuntu 9.10 system, the Slideshow keys for moving the window move it incorrectly.  Shift-RightArrow moves down *and* right, Shift-LeftArrow moves down, Shift-UpArrow moves right, and Shift-DownArrow moves down *and* right. With Alt and the arrow keys, it appears to move in the correct direction with a slight displacement in the incorrect direction moved by Shift.    
